thread.title: Greg Seymour

author: Greg Seymour
title: Greg Seymour
text: My sense was that although one or two agents could offer very cheap management costs, they may not have been linked to very large offices (e.g. with advertising, tenant vetting services etc). I think you 'get what you pay for' and in the end I am very happy that we are paying a bit more but going with Realmark. Thank you for the good service, Greg
